guide za archlinux i windows 11

na linuxu:
	mkdir ~/sharing
	mkdir ~/sharing/write
	mkdir ~/sharing/read
na windowsu:
	Control Panel -> Network and Internet -> Network and Sharing Center -> Change advanced sharing settings:
		sve na on, osim 

sa linuxa na windows:
	na linuxu:
		sudo nano /etc/fstab (dodaj na kraj):
			tmpfs /home/korsic/sharing/write tmpfs defaults,size=2048M 0 0
		sudo mount -t tmpfs tmpfs /home/korsic/sharing/write -o defaults,size=2048M
		sudo pacman -S samba
		sudo nano /etc/samba/smb.conf:
			[global]
				workgroup = WORKGROUP
				server string = Samba Server
				server role = standalone server
				log file = /usr/local/samba/var/log.%m
				max log size = 50
				dns proxy = no
				server smb encrypt = desired
				min protocol = SMB2
				protocol = SMB3
			
			[arch]
				path = /home/korsic/sharing/write
				available = yes
				browsable = yes
				read only = yes
				valid users = korsic
			
		sudo smbpasswd -a korsic
		sudo smbpasswd -a nobody
		sudo ufw allow CIFS
		sudo mkdir /usr/local/samba
		sudo mkdir /usr/local/samba/var
		sudo systemctl start smb nmb
	na windowsu:
		file explorer -> ... -> Map Network Drive:
			Drive							L:
			Folder							\\linux local ip\arch\
			Reconnect at sign-in			on
			login as different user			on
			user:
				korsic

sa windowsa na linux:
	na windowsu:
		ImDisk/RamDisk Configuration:
			Drive Letter					S:
			Allocate Memory Dynamically		on
			File System:					NTFS
			Launch on Windows Startup		on
			Create TEMP folder				false
			Advanced/Drive Label			Sharing
		file explorer -> S: properties -> Security:
			Everyone: 						Read & execute, List folder contents, Read
		file explorer -> S: properties -> Sharing/Advanced Sharing:
			Share this folder				on
			Share name						win11
			max connections					5
			caching							No

na linuxu:
	(default port je 445, ali mozes ostaviti prazno)
	sudo nano /etc/bash.bashrc (dodaj u aliase):
		alias shares='sudo systemctl restart smb; sudo mount -t cifs //<IP_ADDRESS>/win11 /home/korsic/sharing/read -o port=<PORT>,workgroup=WORKGROUP,iocharset=utf8,pass='
